{"tid":773800,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"從400名變考第一　美少女拍拖後發力　如願考入台大醫學系","createTime":"2018-08-10T00:00:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T12:44:45.000Z","uid":81228,"like":179,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"981a8cb8110ce55800a44d2706d636c0f5c446f3","tid":773800,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T00:00:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1732870/org/67fbb163949ad63b5167526c26c8d93d.jpg/Wd_RlifWwgwYJ31nBysx56WcqeYFbSz3vpkyhr6ZMoY?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1732870%2Forg%2F67fbb163949ad63b5167526c26c8d93d.jpg%2FWd_RlifWwgwYJ31nBysx56WcqeYFbSz3vpkyhr6ZMoY%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=8435e62a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誰說中學生不應談戀愛？台灣女高中生一年間成績突飛猛進，從校內400多名衝上第一名，原來全因其「學霸」男友從旁鼓勵和支持，最終她如願考上台大醫學系，惟男友卻只能同校未能同系，其男友決定重考，盼來年能與女友讀同一科，做她的學弟。<br />\n<br />\n這個考生愛情故事備受關注，女主角希望大家了解談戀愛不必然會拖累成績，而自身努力也很重要，她亦希望網民不以閒言議論其男友。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1732175/org/3f346bc65d04dde836900b99d46fd8bf.jpg/16GSh5KATyF-GUkMmA1Og2HUtDyrElYf6f3Enen9xJ0?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1732175%2Forg%2F3f346bc65d04dde836900b99d46fd8bf.jpg%2F16GSh5KATyF-GUkMmA1Og2HUtDyrElYf6f3Enen9xJ0%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=503e1a55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n外表可愛的「女狀元」是高雄女中的應屆考生馮琪淯，是全校唯一一位考上台大醫學系的學生，亦是全校第一名。（facebook「馮琪淯」圖片）<br />\n<br />\n據台灣媒體報道，這名外表可愛的「女狀元」是高雄女中的應屆考生馮琪淯，是全校唯一考上台大醫學系的學生，亦是全校第一名。馮琪淯在台灣的大學入學指定科目考試考取453.55分（理科滿分為500分）。<br />\n<br />\n前日（7日）放榜，其男友得知女友超好成績的喜訊後，一早便到其家向她報喜，本來不抱期望的她，獲知如願考入台大感非常驚喜，遺憾的是其男友雖同樣考入台大，卻考不到醫學系，男友最終決定重考，希望明年可考上和女友一樣的科系成為師弟，馮琪淯則發表愛的宣言：「我會在台大醫科等他。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1732551/org/d2b8f032f3ce554615fb70a8bc939783.png/vbY9BfFEgZKJOnFJQTvdpFkz6vW_W8FwLgaL4C4Gi-A?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1732551%2Forg%2Fd2b8f032f3ce554615fb70a8bc939783.png%2FvbY9BfFEgZKJOnFJQTvdpFkz6vW_W8FwLgaL4C4Gi-A%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=9ef56a79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1732550/org/04bec43fac023e1f64b6d03eb71e7ef6.png/AstIM3nziSc_gIaGpDg9DeGFKU0oHpGSxMBEXcTARF0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1732550%2Forg%2F04bec43fac023e1f64b6d03eb71e7ef6.png%2FAstIM3nziSc_gIaGpDg9DeGFKU0oHpGSxMBEXcTARF0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=d7715a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1732234/org/55291b6f273b4b09850419f64c6aab07.jpg/E1Cd15gPY1-iLaCM5-cL0qi0PO9V7PEVq5IAa6uSAGs?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1732234%2Forg%2F55291b6f273b4b09850419f64c6aab07.jpg%2FE1Cd15gPY1-iLaCM5-cL0qi0PO9V7PEVq5IAa6uSAGs%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c21404e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1732202/org/95e02924819aaf80a30c0b377fe0b1ee.jpg/XMA6TMzQh_HqwJ92HOc9-0CaH9hjqn-CXlSLk15Ui5M?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1732202%2Forg%2F95e02924819aaf80a30c0b377fe0b1ee.jpg%2FXMA6TMzQh_HqwJ92HOc9-0CaH9hjqn-CXlSLk15Ui5M%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=c63f00c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1732204/org/380381beca229dae4f68bcf93e185241.jpg/yfgLIyPw4HL98p4JFtgkg-eA54T_e6is63opV-t6KVc?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1732204%2Forg%2F380381beca229dae4f68bcf93e185241.jpg%2FyfgLIyPw4HL98p4JFtgkg-eA54T_e6is63opV-t6KVc%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b1ebd7d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1732199/org/8ff29fd88f4d67363ff5de183b807950.jpg/7alsISgMFtZ1UfRCBT7LPjol01t6mVC-KpUq3iqVKt4?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1732199%2Forg%2F8ff29fd88f4d67363ff5de183b807950.jpg%2F7alsISgMFtZ1UfRCBT7LPjol01t6mVC-KpUq3iqVKt4%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=d6c8271c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1732198/org/99fe8a5a0cfa43404d87156e807df71f.jpg/8tIZjNZl-tlfHR4PxGrhaiT0VOLjFq9NFJGO0BSRjtA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1732198%2Forg%2F99fe8a5a0cfa43404d87156e807df71f.jpg%2F8tIZjNZl-tlfHR4PxGrhaiT0VOLjFq9NFJGO0BSRjtA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2401a387&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1732201/org/0eb12304ff29605f5c7f2c90471ea2d3.jpg/dvvOTGpTthtfU_gb2WunjuxxpNCT1SOHXRESqF0REqg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1732201%2Forg%2F0eb12304ff29605f5c7f2c90471ea2d3.jpg%2FdvvOTGpTthtfU_gb2WunjuxxpNCT1SOHXRESqF0REqg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f9f3c1d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1732200/org/91d988173a4188817d59ca24218cbf6f.jpg/yWYOJxKX27IvwQdcf3Anrjc7uUguW0joFvvO8Rb7zvE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1732200%2Forg%2F91d988173a4188817d59ca24218cbf6f.jpg%2FyWYOJxKX27IvwQdcf3Anrjc7uUguW0joFvvO8Rb7zvE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=2556c482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1732195/org/5d4e5abfb1c2b16fe3f3d8ebd5796641.jpg/5U0vItY9pdokWBsEfKbWSaoa58jIR3f6vJp8RbyafEU?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1732195%2Forg%2F5d4e5abfb1c2b16fe3f3d8ebd5796641.jpg%2F5U0vItY9pdokWBsEfKbWSaoa58jIR3f6vJp8RbyafEU%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b7d1e5ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1732194/org/4ca92ead7600c4a687940d1dfa6ab7e6.jpg/tmuQMo7KmQv6fM7yrJbnhY1D-TgJt3ay_hOopP4TqKQ?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1732194%2Forg%2F4ca92ead7600c4a687940d1dfa6ab7e6.jpg%2FtmuQMo7KmQv6fM7yrJbnhY1D-TgJt3ay_hOopP4TqKQ%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=0f8f038a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1732196/org/b2f994fd612cefb399afac3d44f77ce2.jpg/moATPrkJ6xkfCaoATQXHi0iHOPwgyPeDAiN-agIjfmo?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1732196%2Forg%2Fb2f994fd612cefb399afac3d44f77ce2.jpg%2FmoATPrkJ6xkfCaoATQXHi0iHOPwgyPeDAiN-agIjfmo%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=fd0fad76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n馮琪淯受訪時指其成績本來很普通，在校內也不過400多名，後來和同為小學同學的男朋友交往，姓魏的男友從小就是「學霸」，經常考全班第一，名列前茅，小情侶在圖書館相伴苦讀，互相督促，成績才逐漸上升，到高二時考入全校前50名，甚至畢業前考到全校第一名。<br />\n<br />\n其後馮琪淯在facebook上發帖提及拍拖和讀書之間的關係，她指「在高一時成績普普，是因為當時我對生活迷茫沒有目標，一直沒有讀書的衝勁，但在升高二的暑假開始意識到必須要振作對未來負責，成績才開始出現我應有的水準」。<br />\n<br />\n她又指自己想證明「談戀愛的確並不必然會拖累成績」，不過也同時強調不必然與成績進步連結在一起，自己努力也重要，「至少在我身上，並不是成績進步的主要、甚至唯一原因。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1732231/org/e47596f4eb2e9a9dc88f69e0ffde97c1.jpg/GjKeshSbCRixJJBuUau84OfwvhAKJdfPyDOSmMgzkpg?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1732231%2Forg%2Fe47596f4eb2e9a9dc88f69e0ffde97c1.jpg%2FGjKeshSbCRixJJBuUau84OfwvhAKJdfPyDOSmMgzkpg%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=ed94373e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n她如願考上台大醫學系，惟男友未能入台大醫學系一同追夢。（facebook「馮琪淯」圖片）<br />\n<br />\n對於男友因為她被過度關注，馮琪淯感到非常抱歉，認為自己的「不成熟和得意忘形的心態造成了傷害」，指男友已經因考不上同一學系而沮喪和難過，認為自己不體貼令男友受到大量閒言閒語、調侃、和他不想要的關注，對此非常的愧疚和懊惱。<br />\n<br />\n她希望大家把注意力集中在「考試路程上的掙扎和煎熬」，又提及自己是比較幸運的一個，感謝父母、師長及同儕的關懷鼓勵。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：謝茜嘉<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/219951/%E5%BE%9E400%E5%90%8D%E8%AE%8A%E8%80%83%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80-%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E6%8B%8D%E6%8B%96%E5%BE%8C%E7%99%BC%E5%8A%9B-%E5%A6%82%E9%A1%98%E8%80%83%E5%85%A5%E5%8F%B0%E5%A4%A7%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8%E7%B3%BB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F219951%2F%25E5%25BE%259E400%25E5%2590%258D%25E8%25AE%258A%25E8%2580%2583%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580-%25